A very simple Perl SDL tower defense game.

To run:

> cd camel-defense/eg
> perl 06-world.pl

What works:

   Can place towers and start waves. Towers fire lasers at creeps within range. Creeps die.

Next tasks:

   Towers cost money. Waves are not infinite. Creeps display their health.

Requires:

   aliased
   SDL
   Moose
   MooseX::Types
   MooseX::Role::BuildInstanceOf


